List all files in a bucket:
aws s3 ls bucket/path/
(final slash is neccessary)
E.g: aws s3 ls my-bucket/path/
Download a file to current local filesystem:
aws s3 cp s3://bucket/path/file local/path
(s3:// is neccessary)
E.g: aws s3 cp s3://my-bucket/path/file.txt .
